'''Townowi''' was a [[Desert/Legends|desert]] [[Planet/Legends|planet]], home of the [[Prince/Legends|princes]] [[Oeta]] and [[Puck Naeco|Puck]] and their older sister [[Zara (princess)|Zara]]. It was threatened with conquest by the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]].

{{Planet-stub}}

==Behind the scenes==
Townowi only appears in the [[The Star Wars first draft|first draft of the script for Star Wars: A New Hope]], replacing [[Aquilae (The Star Wars)|Aquilae]].

It was the source, with slight spelling changes, of the surname of the [[Towani family]] in the films ''[[Caravan of Courage: An Ewok Adventure]]'' and ''[[Ewoks: The Battle for Endor]]''.

